stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> discovered: getDeclaredMarketplaces
    discovered --> pending: 计算 diff（缺失或源地址变更）
    discovered --> up_to_date: diff 结果为 upToDate
    pending --> installing: reconcileMarketplaces 开始
    installing --> installed: 安装成功
    installing --> failed: 安装失败
    installed --> update_check: 下次启动/reload-plugins
    update_check --> up_to_date: 源地址未变
    update_check --> pending: 源地址变更（sourceChanged）
    up_to_date --> [*]
    failed --> [*]
